<chapter id="Account_Details">
  <title>Account Details</title>

  <section condition="TITLE=Account Services: Account Details;PERM=ab_account_details_access"
           id="ASd" role="TOPIC">
    <title>Account Details</title>

    <para role="TEXT">The Account Details option provides the user with
    details of an account linked to a product type account. When the <emphasis
    role="bold">Account Details</emphasis> function is selected, the system
    will display a list of all entities and accounts linked to the
    entities.</para>

    <para role="TEXT">To display the account details:</para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para role="TEXT">On the <guimenu>Account Services</guimenu> menu,
        click <guisubmenu>Account Summary</guisubmenu>. In the
        <guimenu>Account Summary</guimenu> main menu, click
        <guimenuitem>Account Details</guimenuitem>. The <guilabel>Account
        Details</guilabel> page appears. lternatively, if the
        <emphasis>Account Summary</emphasis>, <emphasis>Account
        Statement</emphasis> or <emphasis>Account Details</emphasis> functions
        have already been selected, there will be a link to the <emphasis
        role="bold">Account Details</emphasis> function in the left hand side
        navigation list.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para role="TEXT">In the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> section,
        enter values in the <guilabel>Entity</guilabel> and
        <guilabel>Name</guilabel> fields. To display all records, enter an
        asterisk (*) in any of the criteria fields. Click
        <guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The list of accounts related to an
        entity is displayed. For more information about the search fields and
        the display fields, see the <emphasis>Account Details
        Selection</emphasis> section.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para role="TEXT">Select a record. The <guilabel>List of
        Accounts</guilabel> page appears.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para role="TEXT">In the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> section,
        enter values in the <guilabel>Account Number</guilabel>,
        <guilabel>Currency</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Description</guilabel>
        fields to further refine the list. Click
        <guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The list of accounts matching the
        search criterion is displayed. For more information about the search
        fields and the display fields, see the <emphasis>List of Accounts
        Selection</emphasis> section.</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para role="TEXT">Click the <guilabel>Account Number</guilabel> to
        select a record from the displayed records. The <guilabel>Account
        Details</guilabel> page is displayed. The <guilabel>Entity
        Details</guilabel>, <guilabel>Account</guilabel>, and
        <guilabel>Deposit Account Details</guilabel> of an account are
        displayed. For more information about the fields displayed in this
        section, see the <emphasis>Account Details</emphasis> section.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Account Details Selection</title>

      <para role="TEXT">The <guilabel>Search</guilabel> Options section and
      the results section display the following fields.<informaltable
          role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para
                role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Entity</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">(Editable) Entity mapped to the
                customer.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Name of the
                account.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable></para>
    </section>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>List of Account Selection</title>

      <para role="TEXT">The <guilabel>Search</guilabel> Options section
      displays the following fields.</para>

      <para role="TEXT"><informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para
                role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Entity</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Name of the entity mapped to the
                customer.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Account
                Number</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Reference account number assigned to an
                account in the back office.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Currency</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Currency associated to
                an account.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel>Description
                </guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Additional information
                related to an account.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable></para>

      <para role="TEXT">The results section displays the <guilabel>Account
      Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Currency</guilabel>, and
      <guilabel>Description</guilabel> fields. For the description of fields,
      refer to the description in the <emphasis>Search Options</emphasis>
      section in the <emphasis>List of Accounts Selection</emphasis>
      section.</para>
    </section>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Account Details</title>

      <para role="TEXT">The <guilabel>Account Details</guilabel> section
      displays the following fields.</para>

      <para role="TEXT"><informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para
                role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Account Details</guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"/>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Account
                Number</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">The account number of the required
                statement.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Currency</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The currency of the
                account.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel>Description
                </guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The description for the
                type of account.</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable></para>

      <para role="TEXT">The results section displays the Account Number,
      Currency, and Description fields. For the description of fields, refer
      to the description in the Search Options section in the List of Accounts
      Selection section.</para>

      <para role="TEXT"><informaltable role="TEXT">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Field</para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para
                role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
              </row>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Current Account
                Details</guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"/></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Entity Details</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Entity details in this
                section.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Entity Name </guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Name of the Entity
                linked to the account.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Name </guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The name of the
                account.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Currency </guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The base currency of the
                account.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Entity Abbv
                Name</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Abbreviated name of the Entity.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Account</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Account details in this section.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Account
                Number</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">The account number.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Description</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Description for the account.</entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><guilabel>Status</guilabel></entry>

                <entry valign="top">Status of the account. Status can be
