              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Pooling Enabled</guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Lists whether customer
                account is Pooling enabled or not.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel
                moreinfo="none">Charge Account</guilabel></para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Lists whether customer
